name: What Was It?
Lore: 'When Qui-Gon got away, Maul knew it would only be a matter of time until the two of them would meet again.',
Text: 'If opponent just initiated a duel against one of your non-captive Jedi, deploy on that Jedi. Cancel the duel and relocate this Jedi to an adjacent site. Your duel destiny draws are each +1. (Immune to Control.)',
